<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:12:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，由于兄弟的监管职责，顶级银行家退出中金公司，转投中国主权基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-banker-exiting-cicc-china-sovereign-fund-due-brothers-regulator-role-sources-2024-04-12/</link><description>六位消息人士称，中国国际金融公司（CICC）的一名高管将在退出该投资银行后加入中国主权财富基金中投公司，以避免潜在的利益冲突，因为他的兄弟现在担任中国证券监管机构的负责人。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/top-banker-exiting-cicc-china-sovereign-fund-due-brothers-regulator-role-sources-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国3月铁矿石进口量小幅增长，​​钢材出口量创8年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-march-iron-ore-imports-edge-up-steel-exports-near-8-year-high-2024-04-12/</link><description>周五海关数据显示，中国3月份铁矿石进口量同比增长约0.5%，因预计春节假期后需求将回升，因为钢铁制造商通常会提高产量。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-march-iron-ore-imports-edge-up-steel-exports-near-8-year-high-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国因峰会负面言论召见日本外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-summons-japanese-diplomat-over-negative-comments-summit-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中方周五召见日本外交官，对美日菲领导人峰会期间发表的负面言论表示关切和不满。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:25:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-summons-japanese-diplomat-over-negative-comments-summit-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大贸易展上的关键词是“低价”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-price-is-word-chinas-largest-trade-show-2024-04-12/</link><description>从周一开始，外国买家将涌入中国最大的贸易博览会的广阔大厅，寻找中国商品的交易，美国和欧洲政府抱怨这些商品正在涌入全球市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:19:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/low-price-is-word-chinas-largest-trade-show-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国军队愿与越南提升战略互信水平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-willing-raise-strategic-trust-level-with-vietnam-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国国防部长周五在一份声明中表示，中国国防部长向越南国防部长表示，中国愿意将两军战略互信提升到新水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 08:12:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-willing-raise-strategic-trust-level-with-vietnam-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>德国官员称，肖尔茨将在中国之行中提出俄罗斯产能过剩问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/scholz-will-raise-russia-overcapacity-china-trip-german-officials-say-2024-04-12/</link><description>德国官员周五表示，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨将在访华期间对中国对俄罗斯的支持以及中国产能过剩问题提出担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/scholz-will-raise-russia-overcapacity-china-trip-german-officials-say-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国3月进出口萎缩 大幅低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-march-exports-imports-shrink-miss-forecasts-by-big-margins-2024-04-12/</link><description>周五海关数据显示，中国3月份出口大幅萎缩，进口也意外萎缩，均大幅低于市场预期，突显政策制定者在试图支撑摇摇欲坠的经济复苏时面临的艰巨任务。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-march-exports-imports-shrink-miss-forecasts-by-big-margins-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯媒体称，中国加强对俄罗斯支付的审查，打击电子元件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-tightens-russia-payments-scrutiny-hitting-electronics-components-say-2024-04-12/</link><description>俄罗斯两家新闻媒体周五报道称，俄罗斯公司在向中国付款时面临越来越多的障碍，其中一家称涉及电子零部件的交易受到了影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 07:24:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-tightens-russia-payments-scrutiny-hitting-electronics-components-say-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行将维持政策利率不变，排出部分流动性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-cbank-set-leave-policy-rate-unchanged-drain-some-liquidity-2024-04-12/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国央行周一在展期到期中期贷款时将维持关键政策利率不变，而绝大多数受访者也预计部分流动性将通过债券工具流失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 06:19:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-cbank-set-leave-policy-rate-unchanged-drain-some-liquidity-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋影响力争夺中美中关注所罗门群岛选举</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-election-watched-by-us-china-amid-pacific-influence-contest-2024-04-12/</link><description>所罗门群岛的全国选举是自总理玛纳西·索加瓦雷与北京签署安全协议以来的首次选举，人们将于下周关注其是否有可能撼动中美在南太平洋的竞争。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 05:16:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/solomon-islands-election-watched-by-us-china-amid-pacific-influence-contest-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国探月中继卫星鹊桥二号发射成功</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-launch-relay-satellite-queqiao-2-lunar-probe-mission-successful-2024-04-12/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国国家航天局（CNSA）周五表示，其发射的一颗关键信号中继卫星“取得了圆满成功”，它将作为未来几年月球探测任务的通信桥梁。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 05:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/china-launch-relay-satellite-queqiao-2-lunar-probe-mission-successful-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>中日海警在东海争议海域巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-coast-guards-patrol-disputed-east-china-sea-waters-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国海警周五表示，它在东海钓鱼岛（日本也称为尖阁诸岛）的“领海”进行巡逻。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-coast-guards-patrol-disputed-east-china-sea-waters-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>韩国、日本、美国在朝鲜威胁下举行海军演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-us-hold-naval-drills-amid-nkorea-threats-2024-04-12/</link><description>首尔海军周五表示，韩国、日本和美国举行了计划已久的联合海军演习，其中一艘美国航空母舰参与其中，以确保做好应对朝鲜核威胁和导弹威胁的准备。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 04:28:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-japan-us-hold-naval-drills-amid-nkorea-threats-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>由于交易员削减美联储宽松押注，欧洲股市上涨，美元走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-12/</link><description>周五，欧洲股市有望领先于华尔街，出口商股票需求旺盛，因押注美联储将维持高利率，欧洲大陆主要货币兑美元汇率下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:59:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-12/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国光大集团前董事长被控受贿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-everbright-group-chairman-charged-with-taking-bribes-state-media-2024-04-12/</link><description>中国官方媒体周五报道称，中国光大集团前董事长唐双宁被指控受贿和腐败。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 02:45:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/former-china-everbright-group-chairman-charged-with-taking-bribes-state-media-2024-04-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>